      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Fuse box removal/insertion"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If there are components of the SRS airbag system in the vicinity, refer to the work precautions and configuration drawings described for the SRS airbag system before proceeding."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. 12V battery terminal disconnected",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000910",
          "label": "12V battery terminal disconnected",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Driver lower cover removal",
